{"tid":1781350,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"到底Bandai Namco呢間廠仲可以搞衰幾多個IP","createTime":"2019-12-13T05:46:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T08:29:03.000Z","uid":7232,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"eb481e6b88def8d6a27c686349f7fb191d1a9307","tid":1781350,"uid":7232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:46:16.000Z","msg":"啱啱先知原來上個月東京喰種出咗PS4 game，上Youtube睇下gameplay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SsKlo-dfKek\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSsKlo-dfKek&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6lznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=d2a0a6ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SsKlo-dfKek</a><br />\n<br />\n嘩屌你老母同PS2 PSP年代無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲模組材質差不特止，連啲對白都唔撚改下，1000-7呢句都唔知loop咗幾多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢隻game係第一隻進軍歐美嘅喰種game，但睇留言就知一眾鬼佬已經唔會再俾Bandai呢啲濕尻廠昆，個個喺度屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LhbUnbO7QAU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLhbUnbO7QAU&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6lznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=b97fea06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LhbUnbO7QAU</a><br />\n<br />\n平民呢條片講得好啱，啲日系廠根本就喺度不停咁消費緊自己啲IP，高達已經係一個好好嘅例子<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8a469b94eee8271e23f645dd94e1e6573b20d01","tid":1781350,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:47:38.000Z","msg":"呃傻仔"},{"pid":"e399553fc51dbbf00a731fe127cbeb37781c179c","tid":1781350,"uid":7232,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:48:38.000Z","msg":"好心啲日系廠就反省下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解人哋啲歐美game studio就做得咁好啲日廠就喺度每況愈下，十幾年前啲game真係好好玩，依家真係不知所謂<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y4ubZ2p4IQw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy4ubZ2p4IQw&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6lznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=465030c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y4ubZ2p4IQw</a><br />\n<br />\n之前隻switch隻電車GO諗住可以買嚟重溫下童年回憶，但屌你老母原來係播片，大佬你remaster以前啲CG街景我都無咁嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要收成600，真係省撚返"},{"pid":"b437c2f5c97cfa910b8cd6160ccca22227f89fb9","tid":1781350,"uid":7232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8a469b94eee8271e23f645dd94e1e6573b20d01","tid":1781350,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:47:38.000Z","msg":"呃傻仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:49:15.000Z","msg":"呢樣真，真係買唔撚落（本身漫畫已經爛尾動畫又崩"},{"pid":"51b6ce01d664146346448cb7e01dc001aae59931","tid":1781350,"uid":29130,"like":6,"dislike":7,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:50:27.000Z","msg":"你又唔撚好開口埋口屌日廠捧歐美廠<br />\n<br />\nSekiro deathstranding 呢D日廠黎嫁"},{"pid":"ef60f9687035913ac2239d553fe82da67ecc6a1d","tid":1781350,"uid":7232,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:52:16.000Z","msg":"十幾年前隻Gundam Battle Universe真係良心之作，有成二百幾部UC機任用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要有惡搞extra mission<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ELsB9TTb9PY\" data-sr-url=\"https: